                        <p>Unless you are familiar with the system, dealing with local councils can be confusing. When an application is filled out incorrectly it is often dropped to the bottom of the pile, but we understand what local councils are looking for and handle all the paperwork for you. This can significantly speed up your application and could potentially save you weeks of waiting in frustration.</p>
